## ğŸ§ª Safe Practice Environment

Red teaming must be practiced legally.

Recommended:

- home lab (virtual machines)
- intentionally vulnerable systems
- security lab platforms
- CTF environments

Never attack real systems without permission.

---

## ğŸ§  Beginner Strategy

1. Master Linux terminal
2. Learn networking deeply
3. Understand Windows & Active Directory
4. Practice privilege escalation
5. Break lab machines
6. Read red team writeups
7. Repeat constantly

Skill is built through repetition.

